So there is a difference in behavior.
You are always getting opening and closing form-tag, even if you dont pass a $content to the function.</p>

<p>The Problem is line 73 to 75, where the $content var is set to '' if it is false. (these lines should be deleted)</p>

<p>It should be directly given to the Zend_View_Helper_Form instead. (same behavior)</p>

